// √Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź√Ę‚ÄĘ¬ź
const ctx = $('INIT - Env & Config').first().json;
const items = $input.all();

if (!items.length) return [{ json: { ...ctx, stage: 'GEO_UPSERT_SKIP', count: 0 } }];
if (ctx.DRY_RUN) {
  console.log(JSON.stringify({ stage: 'GEO_UPSERT_DRYRUN', count: items.length }));
  return [{ json: { ...ctx, stage: 'GEO_UPSERT_DRYRUN', count: items.length } }];
}

const records = items.map(i => {
  const r = i.json.record;
  return {
    municipio: r.nombre_municipio,
    provincia: r.nombre_provincia,
    comunidad_autonoma: r.nombre_comunidad || '',
    poblacion: r.poblacion || null,
    latitud: r.latitud || null,
    longitud: r.longitud || null,
    codigo_postal: null,
    slug: r.slug
  };
});

const response = await _fetchPost(`${ctx.SUPABASE_URL}/rest/v1/municipios_dataset_es?on_conflict=slug`, records, {
    'apikey': ctx.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY,
    'Authorization': `Bearer ${ctx.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY}`,
    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
    'Prefer': 'resolution=merge-duplicates,return=minimal'
  });

console.log(JSON.stringify({ stage: 'GEO_UPSERT', batchSize: records.length, status: response.statusCode || 200 }));
return [{ json: { ...ctx, stage: 'GEO_UPSERT_DONE', count: records.length } }];

